2.2p1  Fixed environment variable names
2.2    The Server can now hadle paths with fake filenames. You can use 
       http://i.hdimg.net/o/ZD...H01/the-skate-picture.jpeg instead of
       http://i.hdimg.net/o/ZD...H01.jpeg
       Such filenames are automatically generated in scaled_tag()
       HUIMAGESCOUCHSERVER is now the prefered way to configure the CouchDB.
       HUIMAGESALTADDITION and other stuff for making the software more
       search engine friendly.
2.1    Uploading more than one file at once
2.01   Show ALL tags, not only user tags on an image
2.0    OpenSourced, use Amazon S3 for image storage
